threads.title: 820-00165 no power/ orange light
820-00165 no power/ orange light
threads.message:
More things affected by corrosion.
Did you reball SMC?

Check SPI Bus Series Termination resistors and their traces.
Clean/remove J6100.
Try to start in SMC bypass mode.

threads.title: 820-00165 no power/ orange light
threads.message: It solved. I was in the region of u6100 and the mac called again, thanks.
